{
  "stem": "26728.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I'm credited with a kill and a half, shooting down one and helping shoot down another Me 109.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was over Germany.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, it was-- it was in the vicinity of Schweinfurt, which was a-- a ball-- a ball bearing factory town which the Air Force had been trying to knock out for three or four years.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they would put it out of action temporarily, but they never succeeded in totally shutting it down.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I-- we-- I happened or we happened to run into some German fighters which usually wouldn't engage with us, because they didn't want to sacrifice what few airplanes they had left and what few pilots they had left in dogfights.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They'd rather use those airplanes to shoot down bombers, because that's what they really were after was the bombers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But this particular instance-- I better take-- take a sip here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[DRINKS] This particular instance, we jumped these-- this gaggle of the Me 109s.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They didn't see us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we got some shots on them before they knew we were there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we only got-- the scramble lasted less than 30 seconds, and then they were-- they got-- they left-- they left.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They ran away.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- and-- our-- and we were going to go after them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We had them cold turkey.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We could have got them all.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But our flight leader decided that let's not waste our ammunition on these guys.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They're-- they're not worth-- they're-- we have bigger, bigger, and more important targets than these.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So we just left, and when we were-- we got back to the base and were debriefed, and they used the gun camera's film of each airplane to determine, you know, what happened.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You were-- they'd debrief you by-- with intelligence officers individually asking you what you saw.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
